## warpAffineでアフィン変換

### 並行移動

```elixir
{w, h} = {200, 200}
{x, y} = {50, -10}

m_shift = Nx.tensor([[1, 0, x], [0, 1, y]], type: :f32) |> Cv.Mat.from_nx()
sheer_img = Cv.warpAffine(img, m_shift, {w, h})
```

### 回転

```elixir
{w, h} = {200, 200}
center = {w / 2, h / 2}
angle = 45
scale = 1.0

m_rotate = Cv.getRotationMatrix2D(center, angle, scale)
rotation_img = Cv.warpAffine(img, m_rotate, {w, h})
```

